Wallet > Pool my Funds

User Story

As and end user I need my application to ensure it considers keeping minimum balance, Standing Instructions, Mortgage payments etc., before transferring underutilized funds to the account which doesn't have sufficient funds.

Technical Tasks

On Server side

Task 1: Implementation of an API to trigger a third party target OB system (db-service) to make the transaction.

Task 2: Unit testing/Integration testing.

On UI side

Task 1: Develop screen for Merge Funds where user can select accounts fro which he want to transfer funds and to which the funds need to be transferred.

Task 2 : Preview screen for user to confirm the fund transfer.

Task 3 : Integrating screen with backend services

Task 4: Unit Testing

